      • getTotalVolume

        public double getTotalVolume()
        returns the total volume for the given exercise. The volume of a set is equal to the number of reps performed multiplied by the amount of weight for the set. The total volume is calculated as the sum of the volumes for all sets of the exercise.
        Returns:
        the total volume for the given exercise
